                                    <h5 class="mb-0">
                                        <i class="fa fa-bullseye me-2"></i>
                                        Our Mission
                                    </h5>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <p class="card-text">
                                        To provide quality education that transforms students into competent professionals
                                        and responsible citizens through innovative teaching, research, and community engagement.
