                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                                            <div class="text-center">
                                                <div class="display-1 text-muted mb-2">2020</div>
                                                <h5>Modernization</h5>
                                                <p class="text-muted small">
                                                    Digital transformation and international accreditation achieved.
                                                </p>
                                            </div>
